---
title: Cal Smart Tex-Mex Shrimp Bowls with Texas Caviar and Lime Crema
description: Shrimp never looked so good! Tossed in our smoky signature spice and served up with a hearty portion of black beans, corn, red onion and pepper – known as Texas Caviar, this shrimp dish is sure to please!

